<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/rebecca-harris> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Rebecca Harris was Government Whip (Lord Commissioner of HM Treasury) from 9 January 2018 to 5 July 2024. Rebecca was an Assistant Government Whip in the House of Commons from June 2017 to January 2018. She was elected Conservative MP for Castle Point in May 2010."@en .
